{"tid":1880544,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"謝婉雯 劉永佳 屯院染沙士殉職","createTime":"2020-02-15T02:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T03:15:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"631cb1c64dc4125b6a9e901b9f0f0dacf2cbc441","tid":1880544,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T02:21:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20200215/20862978\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200215%2F20862978&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=90c0431b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200215%2F20862978&h=cc9b80f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20200215/20862978</a><br />\n<br />\n謝婉雯 劉永佳 屯院染沙士殉職<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200215/large/1581698445_7c09.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200215%2Flarge%2F1581698445_7c09.gif&h=1bf5b446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝婉雯（左圖）及劉永佳（右圖）在2003年沙士爆發時不幸染病逝世。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎疫潮被視為「沙士2.0」，屯門醫院是2003年與沙士疫情關係密切的醫院之一，沙士共奪去299條寶貴性命，包括當年於屯門醫院任職胸肺科主任醫生的「香港女兒」謝婉雯。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：香港家居隔離者擅往公院求診<br />\n<br />\n郭家麒轟無吸取教訓<br />\n<br />\n2003年3月，謝婉雯主動要求進入深切治療部救治沙士病人，結果不幸染病，延至5月13日凌晨4時逝世。屯門醫院男護士劉永佳亦因當年4月照顧一名居於淘大花園的沙士病人時，因病人未有申報，劉在毫無防備下受感染，最終殉職。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員郭家麒炮轟醫管局無吸取沙士造成本港近300人包括八名醫護人員死亡的教訓，「明知道對抗疫情，清潔、消毒及隔離最重要，嗰個宿舍污糟到離晒譜，一般人都唔住得啦，更何況醫護人員」。他擔心當局對醫護人員保護掉以輕心，會令醫護處於險境。<br />\n<br />\n■記者譚美芳"},{"pid":"b6e2ae5165a1bf8c45e05385cb119cb757bd8708","tid":1880544,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T02:22:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />rip.</span>"},{"pid":"6f9009af312c3c693cce76847bfad9e6f2bdddd6","tid":1880544,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T02:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392778d66d1912548f03750499f425668853fbe3","tid":1880544,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T02:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f53ce17f6c0428aadb109375c3584c3fee863e","tid":1880544,"uid":129739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T02:26:04.000Z","msg":"血債血償，港共政府"},{"pid":"cdab1c78f8953e2fedc960888a731b82a20f9277","tid":1880544,"uid":75256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T02:26:52.000Z","msg":"謝醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年蘋果頭版報導佢過身，張報紙我仲keep 住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdafbbdb3ab22068252c123e27496489ae1efd47","tid":1880544,"uid":288360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T02:47:26.000Z","msg":"Your spirit is telling us we must close the border."},{"pid":"9d63ae626b8b51ee5eb07866f90abd08fdecd937","tid":1880544,"uid":140666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"631cb1c64dc4125b6a9e901b9f0f0dacf2cbc441","tid":1880544,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T02:21:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20200215/20862978\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200215%2F20862978&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=90c0431b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200215%2F20862978&h=cc9b80f1\" target=\"_blank\"